; Name ..........: VillageSearch
; Description ...: Searches for a village that until meets conditions
; Syntax ........: VillageSearch()
; Parameters ....:
; Return values .: None
; Author ........: Code Monkey #6
; Modified ......: kaganus (Jun/Aug 2015), Sardo 2015-07, KnowJack(Aug 2015)
